possession row and fold the same structure into the next revision:

condition-live freshness, separate authorization and acceptance rows,

explicit long-lived-connection behavior, and evidence status for

partial or open implementation paths.

If you post it, I support the merged row with the boundary above preserved.

Best,

Songbo

